%h4 販売対象
- @books.group("ccode1").sort([["_key"]]).each do |ccode1|
  = link_to("#{ccode1._key} #{ccode1.label} (#{ccode1.n_sub_records})", url(["/search", drilled_params(ccode1: ccode1._key)].join("?")))
  %br
